  "remarks": "Intervesp-M LLC is a Russian company involved in the industrial sector. As part of the “Intervesp Company” group, it supplies machine tools to the Russian market, including to entities active in the Russian military and industrial complex. Therefore, Intervesp-M LLC is supporting Russia’s military and industrial complex, including by being involved in the development, production or supply of military technology and equipment.",
